---
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <hr />
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-bio">
        <span class="section-label">// about</span>
        <h2>A little about me</h2>
        <p>
          I'm a PM at Adobe leading Enterprise features for Adobe Express. Before that,
          years in consulting and Enterprise SaaS — which basically means I've spent a lot
          of time figuring out what people actually need versus what they asked for.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm a dad to two girls, which mostly means I'm outnumbered and okay with it.
          When I'm not working, I'm usually outside — skiing, hiking, or just getting into
          climbing — making something with a pen, or chasing a shot with my camera.
        </p>
        <p>
          I grew up on the early internet. The kind with slow modems, blinking text, and
          the wild feeling that anyone could put anything on a page. That energy still
          shapes how I think about building things.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-facts">
        <dl class="facts-list">
          <div class="fact-row">
            <dt>now</dt>
            <dd>PM Manager, Adobe Express</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <dt>focus</dt>
            <dd>Enterprise + B2B SaaS</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <dt>bg</dt>
            <dd>Consulting → Product</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <dt>outside</dt>
            <dd>Skiing, hiking, climbing</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <dt>making</dt>
            <dd>Photos + pen & ink</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="fact-row">
            <dt>also</dt>
            <dd>Dad × 2</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  hr {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .about-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 260px;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-bio h2 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .about-bio p + p {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
  }

  .facts-list {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .fact-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    padding: var(--space-3) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .fact-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .fact-row:first-child {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  dt {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  dd {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-10);
    }

    .facts-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }

    .fact-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-1);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .fact-row:nth-child(2n) {
      border-right: none;
    }
  }
</style>
